goddesses.name: Baduhenna
goddesses.meaning: Badu-, may be cognate to Proto-Germanic *badwa- meaning battle. The second portion of the name -henna may be related to -henae, which appears commonly in the names of matrons.

goddesses.meaning: Proposed as related to cow, bean, or bee.
